{
  "stem": "20684.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I still remember a big boy-- bigger boy, taller than I.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Similar [INAUDIBLE], but he was so much smarter than me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He also was a survivor from somewhere, but he could speak French so he was a French orphan that survived through the similar circumstance to what I did.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But he was so much smarter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And once, I got the-- I got my best marks on the [INAUDIBLE] I ever got.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We used to go to Paris and we used to play games because we were poor and we didn't have any money when we went to the family.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So we used to do all sorts of things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We could get in-- we'd get into theaters, we'd get into-- I heard Edith Piaf sing in 1949 in the Palais [?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "DeVere ?] for nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We used to go-- we used to go without-- with another family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We pretended that we were part of the other children and when other children sneak through, we used to sneak through.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He taught me how to get in, you now.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Then we'd come in before they had time, we'd sneak through.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But not only that, but we were so smart-- Michel was so smart.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We used to go up to the [FRENCH], which is the very top, the cheapest place, so we know that up there there's always empty seats because people don't go that far.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "That's about the fifth floor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It's called the [FRENCH] in French.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It's the [INAUDIBLE] or whatever you call it in English, I think.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we would watch after the first act to see whether there were some empty seats and we would count them-- we were so smart.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We'd count them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We'd end up sometimes in the best [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
